{
  "texts": [
    "In summary, QLoRA as an adaptation strategy outperforms other adaptation methods.",
    "Specifically, QLoRA Llama2-13B outperforms other models in BLEU score, while achieving comparable performance to Clinical-T5-Large in BERT-Score and ROUGE-L.",
    "Figure 4.4Figure 4. a) Quantitative evaluation metrics across increasing input context lengths.",
    "GPT-4 shows consistency in performance whereas Llama2-13B shows a drop in summarization with increasing context length inputs.",
    "b) Context size analysis for QLoRA Llama2-13B (in/out-of-distribution), where each item on the y-axis displays an independent model fine-tuned on samples from a specific context length range."
